resources NO(60)
notes
Heating experiment to be run in pulsating aurora, aiming at repeating the
HF-enhanced speckles observed at HAARP. Here combined with radar observations of
ionospheric plasma parameters. Likely to be frequently canceled unless
significant substorm activity.

